	<sect1 id="introduction">
		<title>Introduction</title>
		<para>
			&project; is a GNOME2 project that provides integration of 
			<ulink url="http://www.gnupg.org" type="http">Gnu Privacy Guard (GPG)</ulink>
			with the <ulink url="http://www.gnome.org">GNOME</ulink> desktop.
			&project; includes &app;, a GPG key management front end, 
			&daemon;, a drop in replacement for <command>gpg-agent</command> as well as a 
			DNS-SD HKP &key; server, and plug-ins for <guimenuitem>Text Editor
			</guimenuitem> and <application>nautilus</application>.
		</para> 
		<para>
			In <xref linkend="keymanager"/> learn how to perform the following tasks in 
			the Encryption Key Manager:
		</para>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem><para><xref linkend="generate"/></para></listitem>
			<listitem><para><xref linkend="import"/></para></listitem>
			<listitem><para><xref linkend="export"/></para></listitem>
			<listitem><para><xref linkend="backup"/></para></listitem>
			<listitem><para><xref linkend="key-properties"/></para></listitem>
			<listitem><para><xref linkend="key-server"/></para></listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
		<para>
			In <xref linkend="file-manager"/> learn how to perform the following tasks 
			in the File Manager:
		</para>		
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem><para><xref linkend="encrypt-fm"/></para></listitem>
			<listitem><para><xref linkend="sign-fm"/></para></listitem>
			<listitem><para><xref linkend="decrypt-fm"/></para></listitem>
			<listitem><para><xref linkend="verify-fm"/></para></listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
		<para>
			In <xref linkend="text-editor"/> learn how to perform the following tasks in 
			<guimenuitem>Text Editor</guimenuitem>:
		</para>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem><para><xref linkend="encrypt-te"/></para></listitem>
			<listitem><para><xref linkend="sign-te"/></para></listitem>
			<listitem><para><xref linkend="decrypt/verify-te"/></para></listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
		<!-- note>Most &key; management features can be found in the <xref linkend="key-properties"/>.</note -->
	</sect1>
